<section>
    <h2 class="page-header" id="blockquote">Blockquotes</h2>
    <p>For quoting blocks of content from another source within your document.</p>

	<section>
		<h3 class="page-header" id="blockquote-options">Blockquote options</h3>
		<p>
			Wrap <code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> around any <abbr title="HyperText Markup Language">HTML</abbr> as the quote. We recommend the use of <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> inside of <code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code>.
		</p>

		<blockquote>
			<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.</p>
		</blockquote>

		<div class="mrgn-tp-lg">
			<pre><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></pre>
		</div>

		<div class="row wb-eqht mrgn-tp-lg mrgn-bttm-xl">
			<section class="col-md-6">
				<h4 class="mrgn-tp-0 text-success">Use when <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-circle"></span></h4>
				<p>(Info goes here)</p>
			</section>

			<section class="col-md-6 brdr-lft">
				<h4 class="mrgn-tp-0 text-danger">Do not use when <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove-circle"></span></h4>
				<p>(Info goes here)</p>
			</section>
		</div>

		<section>
			<h4>Naming a source</h4>
			<p>Add a <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> for identifying the source. Wrap the name of the source work in <code>&lt;cite&gt;</code>.</p>

			<blockquote>
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.</p>
				<footer>Someone famous in <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite></footer>
			</blockquote>

			<div class="mrgn-tp-lg">
				<pre><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;footer&gt;Someone famous in &lt;cite title="Source Title"&gt;Source Title&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/footer&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></pre>
			</div>

			<div class="row wb-eqht mrgn-tp-lg mrgn-bttm-xl">
				<section class="col-md-6">
					<h5 class="mrgn-tp-0 text-success h4">Use when <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-circle"></span></h5>
					<p>(Info goes here)</p>
				</section>

				<section class="col-md-6 brdr-lft">
					<h5 class="mrgn-tp-0 text-danger h4">Do not use when <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove-circle"></span></h5>
					<p>(Info goes here)</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h4>Alternate displays</h4>
			<p>Use <code>blockquote-reverse</code> for a floated, right-aligned blockquote.</p>

			<blockquote class="blockquote-reverse">
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante.</p>
				<small>Someone famous in <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite></small>
			</blockquote>
			<div class="clearfix"></div>

			<div class="mrgn-tp-lg">
				<pre><code>&lt;blockquote class=&quot;blockquote-reverse&quot;&gt;
	...
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></pre>
			</div>

			<div class="row wb-eqht mrgn-tp-lg mrgn-bttm-xl">
				<section class="col-md-6">
					<h5 class="mrgn-tp-0 text-success h4">Use when <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-circle"></span></h5>
					<p>(Info goes here)</p>
				</section>

				<section class="col-md-6 brdr-lft">
					<h5 class="mrgn-tp-0 text-danger h4">Do not use when <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove-circle"></span></h5>
					<p>(Info goes here)</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</section>
	</section>
</section>

<section>
    <h2 class="page-header" id="inline">Inline quotes</h2>
    <p>For phrasing content quoted from another source. Use <code>&lt;&gt;</code> if a quotation is short and appears within a paragraph.</p>
	
	<p>"<q>Our Government is committed to protecting livestock health</q>" said Minister Ritz.</p>

	<div class="mrgn-tp-lg">
		<pre><code>&lt;p&gt;"&lt;q&gt;Our Government is committed to protecting livestock health&lt;/q&gt;" said Minister Ritz.&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre>
